## Algorithm track

### Research directions
- Phylogenomic algorithm development
- Algorithm optimization

### Requirements
- Demonstrated ability to program in C++.
- (PKU student) Completed [Bioinformatics Algorithms in Evolutionary Biology](../../teaching/bioinformatics-algorithms-in-evolutionary-biology).
- (Non-PKU student) Completed [ASTER OpenJudge practice problems](http://aster.openjudge.cn/practice/).

### Application

Please send your Resume/CV and your **OpenJudge account information** to ASTER LAB E-mail.

## Bioinformatic track

### Research directions
- Phylogenomic reconstruction
- Ancient gene flow detection

### Requirements
- Experience in phylogenomic analysis or a strong background in systematics.
- Ability to conduct independent research under general guidance.

### Application

Please send your resume/CV with **experience in phylogenomics and/or or background in systematics clearly highlighted** to ASTER LAB E-mail.